text: Elizabeth Island may refer to: * Elizabeth Island (Alaska) * Elizabeth Island, Bahamas * Elizabeth Island, Bermuda * Elizabeth Island (Georgian Bay) * Elizabeth Island, Michigan * Elizabeth Island, New Zealand * Elizabeth Island (Victoria) * Elizabeth Island (Cape Horn), possibly the same as Pactolus Bank * A small cay rising above sea level at Elizabeth Reef in the Coral Sea Islands, Australia * An early alternative name for Henderson Island (Pitcairn Islands) Or may refer to the Elizabeth Islands chain in Massachusetts, USA
title: Elizabeth Island
